            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A remnant who are willing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To come and work in Your house,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, what a blessed charge!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your heart’s desire, is our desire—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
